last_episode_to_air.name: I’m Not Going Back To Siesta Key
last_episode_to_air.overview: Juliette has one last Miami JMP event, and if it’s not successful, she’s back in Siesta Key. Sam and Jordana confront their feelings even with the looming faux fur business launch. Amanda and Chloe try to save their friendship before the summer ends.

name: Siesta Key
overview: Docuseries following a group of young adults confronting issues of love, heartbreak, betrayal, class, and looming adulthood as they spend the summer together in their beautiful hometown.

episodes.name: Romeo and Juliette
episodes.overview: Alex, the leader of the pack, finds himself stuck in the middle of a love triangle between Madisson, his high school sweetheart, and Juliette, his old flame from last summer.

episodes.name: We Need to Talk About Chloe
episodes.overview: Chloe copes with a huge blow from one of her best friends over Siesta’s heartthrob, Brandon.

episodes.name: Kelsey's New Crew
episodes.overview: Garrett’s jealousy builds as Alex and Kelsey get a bit too friendly on the boat. Kelsey welcomes the attention and wonders whether she sees a future with Garrett. Chloe tries to face up to her destructive behavior.

episodes.name: Alex's Kingdom
episodes.overview: Alex deals with the repercussions of his fling with Amanda and debates whether or not to tell Juliette. Madisson steps away from the battle for Alex and catches Brandon’s eye. Kelsey and Garrett grow further apart.

episodes.name: Madisson’s Avenues
episodes.overview: Rumors catch fire about Kelsey and Alex in a hot tub just as Garrett and Kelsey reach a crossroads. Madisson and Brandon strike a spark while Chloe considers her relationship with Amanda.

episodes.name: Juliette's Bahama Drama
episodes.overview: The crew visits Bimini for some days of fun; drama rapidly spreads when evidence of Alex and Kelsey's indiscretions come to light; jealously overwhelms Juliette; Madisson and Brandon continue to get comfortable with each other.

episodes.name: Messy Messy Kelsey
episodes.overview: Kelsey continues to weave a messy web between Alex and Garrett. Juliette reevaluates her relationship with Alex. Chloe takes a break from the group. Madisson receives a proposal from her ex that casts a cloud of doubt on her future with Brandon.

episodes.name: Garrett Gets a Girl
episodes.overview: Garrett is in denial about Kelsey and Alex; Juliette flirts with Garrett, and considers spilling the beans; Pauly spends the night in jail; Chloe throws a party.

episodes.name: Chloe at a Crossroads
episodes.overview: Things heat up with Juliette and Garrett just as Alex starts to pull away from Kelsey. Alex tries to make things right with Chloe while Brandon and Madisson take their relationship to the next level. Pauly catches a break with a major gig.

episodes.name: Juliette's Midsummer Dream
episodes.overview: Juliette's cruel intentions take a turn; Kelsey's bad decisions catch up with her; Madisson tells Alex how she feels; Pauly pushes Chloe.

episodes.name: Much Ado About Juliette
episodes.overview: Alex gets in a bar fight that leaves his jaw wired shut; and Juliette questions Garrett’s loyalty after a questionable night with Kel.

episodes.name: Chloe’s Birthday Battle Royale
episodes.overview: Tensions reach an all-time high at Chloe's birthday. Madisson confronts Canvas, Garrett is unable to stay away from Kelsey, and Juliette takes comfort in the familiar arms of Alex.

episodes.name: Juliette, Interrupted
episodes.overview: Kelsey receives a modeling opportunity that sends her packing for NYC; Bradisson attempt to get their relationship back on track; Juliette heads back to school, but her happy arrival quickly turns into a nightmare.

episodes.name: Kelsey's Reality Bites
episodes.overview: Rumors emerge about Juliette and Alex; Kelsey and Madisson head off to New York to pursue their careers, but a rude awakening awaits them; Brandon makes a choice that forever changes the course of Bradisson.

episodes.name: Nightmare on Bradisson Street
episodes.overview: Juliette reveals her rekindled relationship to the group; Kelsey and Garret continue to bond; Tarik opens up about his sexuality; Brandon struggles with his infidelities as Chloe and Canvas dig for the truth.

episodes.name: Take a Paige From Canvas
episodes.overview: Kelsey tries to reignite things with Garrett, but a new love interest occupies his attention; Hannah continues to meddle in Juliette's relationship; an unexpected romance blossoms.

episodes.name: Alex Won't Kompomise
episodes.overview: Paige breaks the news to Madisson about her unexpected romance with Canvas; Brandon is devastated when Madisson brings her new squeeze Ben to Alex's housewarming party; Alex and Hannah's feud comes to a head.

episodes.name: Juliette's Great Expectations
episodes.overview: Brandon makes a final emotional play to get Madisson back; Kelsey reveals her feelings to Garrett, only to be blocked by an unforeseen obstacle; Juliette and Alex have an explosive fight that leaves JAlex's future uncertain.

episodes.name: Born a King.
episodes.overview: Juliette’s parents and Alex's parents meet, Madisson is unsure about her future with Ben, and Alex's birthday party goes off the rails when uninvited guests show up.

episodes.name: Your Own Hairdresser!
episodes.overview: Jared and Pauly sit down to discuss the birthday party brawl, Chloe confronts Juliette, Alex reveals a secret, and friendships are tested.

episodes.name: Sorry! I Don't Owe You Anything
episodes.overview: Sparks fly and tempers flare during a 70s-themed party, Garrett goes on a date with someone unexpected, Alex gives Chloe an ultimatum, and Brandon's relationship is tested.

episodes.name: How Am I a Lot to Handle?!
episodes.overview: Chloe learns that her friendship with Cara may not be as genuine as she thought

episodes.name: A Second Tier Friend...
episodes.overview: After days of turmoil for Jalex, Juliette witnesses something that could change her and Alex forever; Madisson stars in Brandon's music video, causing issues in her relationship with Ben and prompting jealousy from Brandon's girlfriend.

episodes.name: It's Been a Day
episodes.overview: Juliette struggles with the news of Alex and the two girls in his bed; Chloe learns that Ben has been sexting Tawni behind Madisson's back and hatches a plan to catch him in the act; Brandon's girlfriend's jealousy reaches an all-time low.

episodes.name: Deflect, Deflect, Deflect
episodes.overview: Juliette receives some shocking information from a surprising source; Garrett and Cara take a huge step in their relationship; Jared struggles to assimilate by using alcohol to escape his past; Pauly gets arrested on a felony charge.

episodes.name: Cheers to Sunday Funday!
episodes.overview: With Jalex on the rocks, Alex connects with an old flame. Madisson reaches her breaking point with Ben. Brandon sets out on tour as a single man and is pleasantly surprised by who shows up at his concert.

episodes.name: I Had High Hopes for You.
episodes.overview: Garrett and Cara's relationship is tested; Brandon and Jared compete for Madisson's affection; Pauly faces consequences for his arrest and takes steps to earn his way back into Grandma's good graces.

episodes.name: I Want Him (Without the Cheating).
episodes.overview: Juliette turns 21 years old and Alex tries to buy his way back into her life with an extravagant present; Garret and Cara are already at a crossroads when Garrett reveals a job opportunity that puts their relationship in jeopardy.

episodes.name: Cheers to the End of Summer!
episodes.overview: Pauly tries to defend Alex and stirs up drama at Cara's end-of-summer bash; Chloe shares some findings with Juliette that make her rethink everything she knows to be true; Cara loses her cool with Garrett.

episodes.name: What Are Your Real Intentions With Juliette?
episodes.overview: Juliette looks for a fresh start with a new man, everyone is shocked by Madisson's familiar new boyfriend, and Cara and Garrett try to pick up the pieces.

episodes.name: New Man, Who Dis?
episodes.overview: Madisson introduces Ish to her father, Cara and Garrett reach a crossroads in their relationship, and tempers flare when Juliette and Chloe discuss their fractured friendship.

episodes.name: Where's My Apology?
episodes.overview: Chloe considers legal action against Juliette, Madisson worries about Brandon, the lines are blurred in Garrett and Cara's relationship, and Alex returns from Europe.

episodes.name: Are You Offended? Because You Should Be!
episodes.overview: Juliette has to choose between her new job or going to Greece with her new boyfriend, Robby. Alex makes a play for a newly single Cara. Brandon and Amanda’s budding romance is threatened by Madisson and Amanda’s ex, JJ.

episodes.name: Why Are You With Somebody Who Doesn't Deserve You?
episodes.overview: Juliette tries to clear the air with Alex and make amends with Chloe and Amanda, Kelsey raises eyebrows with someone new, and Alex brings a date to Amanda's party.

episodes.name: Are You Happy With Her?
episodes.overview: Juliette has second thoughts about her future with Robby, Kelsey's friendship with Jake raises eyebrows, Robby offers Amanda an apology, and Brandon grows suspicious.

episodes.name: What's Really Going On With You And Alex?
episodes.overview: Madisson worries about a life-altering possibility, Alex sends personal texts to Robby, Jared anticipates a call from his ex, and Juliette faces off with Alex and Alyssa.

episodes.name: So You're The Ex-Wife?
episodes.overview: Jared's ex-wife Jessica comes to Florida, Chloe gets in the middle of the drama between Alex and Juliette, and Brandon confronts JJ and Amanda about their flirting.

episodes.name: Why Don't You Just Mind Your Own Damn Business?
episodes.overview: Juliette tries to avoid drama, Alex and Amanda question Chloe's intentions, and Madisson's future with Ish is jeopardized by her family's disapproval.

episodes.name: Are you stalking me?
episodes.overview: Juliette clears the air with Robby, Alex catches Juliette by surprise, Kelsey receives unexpected news, Blend's grand opening is filled with drama, and Chloe plays peacemaker.

episodes.name: What if it goes completely south?
episodes.overview: When the gang goes to Nashville to support BG's music, old flames reignite, Alex explodes over Pauly's meddling, and tensions between Juliette, Chloe and Amanda boil over.

episodes.name: Where did you sleep last night?
episodes.overview: Juliette wrestles with her guilt, Alex tries to quell Alyssa's suspicions, Chloe makes a deal, and Madisson catches up with Cara while visiting Ish in New York City.

episodes.name: I’m Not Letting Him Get Away With It
episodes.overview: Juliette wants to come clean to Alyssa about Nashville. Chloe is caught between her loyalty to Juliette and her career. Amanda chooses sides, betraying Juliette in the process.

episodes.name: I'm Not Asking For Any Judgment
episodes.overview: Garrett sends Kelsey mixed signals, Jared's girlfriend butts heads with Chloe, Robby tries to reconnect with Juliette, and Madisson defends her relationship.

episodes.name: I'm Ready for a Good Guy
episodes.overview: Brandon reconnects with his former flame Camilla, Amanda and JJ struggle to trust each other, Juliette contemplates a new romance, and Alyssa learns life-changing news.

episodes.name: I'm Gonna Be Drunk For The Next Week
episodes.overview: Brandon puts his dreams on hold, Chloe feels overwhelmed at work, Madisson pursues acting, and Juliette is shocked when she finds out Alyssa is pregnant.

episodes.name: I Just Didn't Think It Was Going to Happen So Fast
episodes.overview: Juliette takes on a daunting work assignment, Chloe's meddling threatens her friendship with Madisson, and Kelsey's future with Garrett is jeopardized by her ex.

episodes.name: I'm Thankful
episodes.overview: Madisson distances herself from the group, Alyssa's mom worries about her daughter's relationship, and unresolved feuds take center stage at Chloe's Friendsgiving dinner.

episodes.name: I Want Him To Have A Girl
episodes.overview: Old friends are forced to choose a side as Juliette grows closer to Sam, Amanda and JJ make a decision about their future together, and Alyssa finds out her baby's gender.

episodes.name: Can I Talk To You For a Second?
episodes.overview: During the Christmas season, Juliette and Sam become more than just friends, Camilla uses a gift to pressure Brandon to commit, and Chloe blames Ish for her feud with Madisson.

episodes.name: I Didn't Even Know That You Were That Into Bathing Suits
episodes.overview: The crew spends New Year's Eve in Miami, Madisson and Ish go house hunting, Kelsey grows frustrated over Juliette's business venture, and Camilla doesn't like Amanda flirting with Brandon.

episodes.name: I'm Falling For Sam
episodes.overview: Kelsey and Madisson share shocking news with Ashley, Juliette and Kelsey's friendship is strained, Garrett launches a supplement line, and Amanda calls out JJ.

episodes.name: I'm Actually Like Happy
episodes.overview: Brandon faces a decision about his future, Madisson surprises her friends and family with an announcement, and Kelsey questions Juliette's intentions.

episodes.name: Reunion
episodes.overview: Jeannie Mai hosts as the Siesta Key cast virtually looks back at breakups, makeups and blowups from Season 3, and the group shares relationship updates, shocking secrets and more.

episodes.name: Let's Be Healthy and Get Drunk
episodes.overview: Brandon embraces fatherhood, Chloe reinvents herself, Madisson worries about the age difference in her relationship, Amanda holds a film screening, and Kelsey confronts Juliette.

episodes.name: It's a Nasty, Low Vibrational Thing to Say
episodes.overview: Chloe tries to repair broken friendships, Kelsey shares a joke that creates a bigger rift with Juliette, and Sam commissions a painting that leaves everyone speechless.

episodes.name: Here's the Thing with the Prenup...
episodes.overview: Madisson considers a prenup after a discussion with her father, Camilla and Brandon rehash their difficult past, and Chloe struggles to find support from Amanda and Juliette.

episodes.name: I Can't Help if Someone Is Attracted to Me
episodes.overview: Camilla's flirting leads Brandon to a confrontation, Juliette works out the details of her swimsuit line, and Madisson's anxiety rears its head as everyone prepares for an island vacation.

episodes.name: Happy to See Me, Right?
episodes.overview: Chloe makes a shocking announcement, Camilla confronts Brandon about hooking up with Jordana, Amanda is caught between Juliette and Kelsey, and Madisson invites Cara to the island.

episodes.name: You Don't Seem Like the Caring Type
episodes.overview: Cara makes waves when she tries to make amends with the group, Sam and Juliette don't see eye to eye, Garrett shows his romantic side, and tempers flare at Kelsey's swimwear photoshoot.

episodes.name: Things Will Never Be the Same
episodes.overview: Joe and Stef discuss their complicated situationship, Brandon's music video premiere party goes off the rails, and Juliette loses control and shocks everyone.

episodes.name: That Girl Is Lost
episodes.overview: After Juliette's sudden departure, the vibe on the island changes, Amanda and Tate grow closer, Kelsey and Garrett see a different side of Cara, and Madisson focuses on her mental health.

episodes.name: Compassion And Kindness Is The Way To Go
episodes.overview: Madisson makes a big decision about her wedding, Brandon throws a baby shower for Quincy, and Chloe returns with hopes of mending Juliette's and Kelsey's friendship.

episodes.name: I'm Truly, Truly, Very, Very Sorry
episodes.overview: Juliette takes charge of her business and hopes to make amends with Kelsey, Jordana wants more from Brandon, and Sam has a request for Juliette as they celebrate their one-year anniversary.

episodes.name: We Can All Use a Little Empathy
episodes.overview: At Madisson's empathy-themed birthday party, Chloe's apology to Cara falls flat, then Juliette considers moving in with Sam, and Tate's secret online life goes public.

episodes.name: I Just Want to Move On/We Just Stay Separate
episodes.overview: Chloe hosts an astrology-themed event, Brandon ponders his custody options, Kelsey is uncomfortable at Juliette's swimwear launch party, and Amanda loses patience with Tate's dishonesty.

episodes.name: 24 and Still a Mess
episodes.overview: Juliette is worried about her relationship as she considers moving out of Sam's house; Chloe has a new boyfriend to impress, but issues with Jordana and Cara test her; Brandon apologizes to Camilla for his past indiscretions.

episodes.name: You ARE The Rich Husband!
episodes.overview: As Juliette takes steps to move out, her relationship with Sam worsens. Kelsey is lonely in the key. Chloe worries that the groups’ drama will scare Chris away. Jordana throws an art show revealing a deeper side of her.

episodes.name: Do You Even Want To Try?
episodes.overview: Juliette and Sam’s tension finally reaches its breaking point. Madisson is overwhelmed when she begins to prep for the wedding. Brandon thinks he’s ready to hang out with the group again, but he’s concerned about seeing Jordana.

episodes.name: He Doesn't See a Future
episodes.overview: Juliette is shocked that Sam moves on so quickly after their break up; the whole group chooses sides between Juliette and Sam, especially Jordana and Cara; Kelsey wonders about life outside of Florida, but Max is hesitant.

episodes.name: Deux Chardonnay
episodes.overview: Juliette wants to get over Sam while she’s in Paris, but it’s not as easy as she hoped. Sam introduces Meghan to the group among unaccepting friends. Kelsey and Will are concerned about Garrett and Kenna’s relationship.

episodes.name: Stop Texting Me, Stop Calling Me
episodes.overview: Juliette thinks she’s over Sam, but seeing him move on with other women changes everything. Brandon struggles with figuring out custody arrangements with Delainey. Cara is frustrated that Michael hasn’t said “I love you” yet.

episodes.name: Stop Videotaping
episodes.overview: Juliette is hesitant about rekindling things with Sam. Brandon juggles his son, career, Delainey, and a new relationship. Lexie is stuck in the middle of supporting her best friend, Juliette and her boyfriend’s best friend, Sam.

episodes.name: I Was Living A Lie With Him
episodes.overview: Juliette’s friends disapprove of her getting back with Sam, and she has to make a difficult decision. Sam and Chloe have conflicting ideas about what’s best for Juliette. Chloe contemplates taking the next big step with Chris.

episodes.name: Someone Sent A Video
episodes.overview: The girls visit Madisson in LA. A video of Juliette and a mystery guy makes its way around the group. Sam moves on from Juliette, and it brings him back to a familiar face. Kelsey struggles with her relationship and a possible career change.

episodes.name: Where’s The Popcorn?
episodes.overview: Juliette tries to be civil with Sam, but Meghan’s return and Mike’s insults push her to the limit. Amanda’s dad’s health scare makes her reprioritize life. Garrett’s plans to live with Kenna threatens his friendship with Will.

episodes.name: You’re Moving?
episodes.overview: Tension between Team Juliette and Team Sam threatens to disrupt Madisson’s wedding. Juliette starts to figure out the next big step for JMP but is overwhelmed by the pressure. Sam contemplates a fresh start elsewhere.

episodes.name: Tiny
episodes.overview: Words are exchanged when the group gathers for Madisson and Ish’s wedding; Juliette, Sam and their new partners have an awkward run-in; and Kelsey and Max’s relationship reaches an impasse.

episodes.name: Season 4A Reunion
episodes.overview: Rachel Lindsay chats with the Siesta Key gang about Madisson's big announcement, Chloe's desire to change her ways, Brandon's role as a dad, and Kelsey and Juliette's memorable fight.

episodes.name: Welcome to Miami
episodes.overview: Ready to take on Miami, Juliette leaps into this new world, but finds herself feeling alienated from Chloe and Amanda. Sam and Jordana's complex relationship is questioned. Brandon feels the pressure to take the next step.

episodes.name: You Are in a Huge Pond Now
episodes.overview: Juliette continues to shut out Chloe and Amanda as JMP the Label evolves. Between Meghan's ultimatum and Jordana's BBL, Sam's attention is split. Brandon is given a shot at proving himself in front of a music industry legend.

episodes.name: Ask Your Best Friend
episodes.overview: Juliette finds out that Meghan has been spreading a rumor about her relationship. Sam sabotages himself when he is pressured to decide what to do about the ultimatum. Brandon's new romantic interest starts to interfere.

episodes.name: He Was Flirting With Her
episodes.overview: Juliette seeks the truth regarding Meghan’s rumor that Clark flirts with her. Sam and Jordana are forced to deal with the aftermath of their scandalous kiss. Lexie and Mike's relationship crumbles as gossip about inappropriate behavior emerges.

episodes.name: We Gotta Put On A Good Show
episodes.overview: As Juliette prepares for Miami Swim Week, the pressure is on to make JMP the Label successful. Jordana faces criticism when friends worry that Sam’s lifestyle is corrupting her. Kelsey visits Miami and begins to fix her friendship with Juliette.

episodes.name: This TV Show Changed You
episodes.overview: Juliette’s ready for a vacation after Swim Week, but she finds out that’s the wrong move. Cara launches her jewelry line, but her fight with Jordana weighs on her. Madisson visits to receive support from her friends as she grieves the loss of Elliot.

episodes.name: Our Best Friend's Ex-Boyfriend's Shirt
episodes.overview: Kelsey and Chloe argue over Jordana illustrating Madisson's book, creating friction in the whole group; Chloe thinks Amanda is disrespecting Juliette by hanging out with Sam; new information further complicates Mike and Lexie's relationship.

episodes.name: He’s Never Picked You
episodes.overview: When Juliette returns from Greece, she discovers how much has changed with her friends since she left. Jordana’s mom visits, and Sam strives to show her how much Jordana means to him. Kelsey has big news about her future with the group.

episodes.name: How Do You Know It's Toxic?
episodes.overview: Juliette and Chloe become frustrated by Amanda's disloyal actions; Jordana and Sam's relationship is strained when Jordana finally starts listening to the words of wisdom from her friends.

episodes.name: It's Not About The Bathing Suit
episodes.overview: Juliette, Chloe, and Amanda try to recover from their fight, but not everyone is ready to move on. Jordana and Sam continue to have issues with their living situation. Brandon tells Teenear and her dad about his record label opportunity.

episodes.name: Is It Worth The Risk?
episodes.overview: Juliette continues her struggle to mend the friendship between her, Chloe, and Amanda. Jordana reveals that she has feelings for Sam, and he doesn’t know how to react. Chloe makes a big push for her company’s future.

episodes.name: I’m Not Going Back To Siesta Key
episodes.overview: Juliette has one last Miami JMP event, and if it’s not successful, she’s back in Siesta Key. Sam and Jordana confront their feelings even with the looming faux fur business launch. Amanda and Chloe try to save their friendship before the summer ends.
